                            Label: "battle_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "Not yet",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "I have panned this desert for anything worth keeping. A strong challenger is a rare find. Care to prove you are one?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Last of the diggers. Beat me and the apprentice will see you. Ready?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The claim itself is not for sale. It has sedimental value - that is when the worth is down in the layers, where it belongs."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "(He bites a coin, frowns, and pockets it.) Habit. Hard to trust a mint mark since the grey suits came sniffing at the fields."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Vince - warden of the inner cut",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
